# ── Planning / personal notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Project docs that help developers understand the codebase live in docs/ and
# stay tracked (architecture.md, features.md, api.md, tools.md, frontend.md,
# dev.md). Personal planning — sprint notes, critiques, proposals, strategy
# brainstorms, ideas, todos — stays local. Drop them in local_debugging/ (above)
# or use one of the suffixes below.
ideas.md
docs/*-sprint.md
docs/*_critique*.md
docs/*_proposal*.md
docs/*_philosophy*.md
docs/*_strategy*.md
